// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2022-1670 — Mass File Rename (icefire)
// Status: deprecated | Level: high | ID: 88b57461-1dd9-574e-86bb-8911de65ada5

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
